We can pre-schedule the messages that will be send on specific days automatcally.

There are so many platforms provide thses API services to users.

We used Vonage which was known as Nexmo before.

After installing 'curl' on our machine. we just need to write the following command(sudo apt install curl)

curl -X POST  https://rest.nexmo.com/sms/json \

-d api_key=......\

-d api_secret= 	........\		#key and secret are given to user after signup on their website

-d to=123456789 \           #phone number where the messahe to be sent

-d from=14037741329 \	      #number provided by Vinage

-d text="Type your message here"
